OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FMichelle Agyemang tells ITV News
OL,8,FSports Editor Steve Scott about her
OL,9,Fexhilarating England debut, and how
OL,10,Fher deep faith has helped her through
OL,11,Fa long recovery from an ACL tear as
OL,12,Fshe prepares for 2027's World Cup in
OL,13,FBrazil.
OL,15,FFor someone who was a teenager just a
OL,16,Ffew weeks ago, Michelle Agyemang
OL,17,Fpossesses an air of composure and
OL,18,Fmaturity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FThis is all the more remarkable given
OL,8,Fthe year she's had; life-changing
OL,9,Fhighs punctuated by the cruel lows
OL,10,Fshe's currently working through.
OL,12,FA couple of weeks ago, Agyemang was
OL,13,Fallowed to throw her crutches away,
OL,14,Ffour months after rupturing her
OL,15,Fanterior cruciate ligament (ACL) while
OL,16,Fplaying for the Lionesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,F"It's nice to be back on my feet,
OL,8,Fwalking again," she told me. "And I'm
OL,9,Fprogressing every day, which is good.
OL,10,FI think every sort of rehab is going
OL,11,Fto be difficult.
OL,13,F"No one said it was going to be easy,
OL,14,Fso I'm getting through it well, and
OL,15,FI've got a lot of support around me."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@OO]pD@^OUuD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FThat support includes Arsenal and
OL,8,FEngland teammates Beth Mead and Leah
OL,9,FWilliamson. Both have had the same
OL,10,Fserious injury, and after a long,
OL,11,Flonely time rehabilitating, managed to
OL,12,Fmake it back onto the international
OL,13,Fstage.
OL,15,F"To see them every day, they know what
OL,16,Fwe're going through and, sometimes, to
OL,17,Fgive us little tips, handy things that
OL,18,Fcan help us, you know, better our
OL,19,Frecovery and enhance it.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,F"It's obviously difficult, but it's
OL,8,Fsomething you need to go through to
OL,9,Fget back to where I want to be, which
OL,10,Fis playing football again every week
OL,11,Fin, week out."
OL,13,FI met Agyemang as she headed to
OL,14,Funiversity lectures in London, where
OL,15,Fshe's studying for a business
OL,16,Fmanagement degree.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FBefore we discussed her breakout year,
OL,8,Fshe revealed another hidden talent,
OL,9,Fsitting at the stool of a Steinway
OL,10,Fpiano and expertly playing her
OL,11,Ffavourite hymn, "Great is thy
OL,12,Ffaithfulness".
OL,14,FMusic, she says, particularly gospel
OL,15,Fmusic, takes her to a calm place which
OL,16,Fin turn helps her with everything from
OL,17,Fthe pressure of international football
OL,18,Fto the seemingly endless road back to
OL,19,Ffitness.
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,F"Music is very important. I've grown
OL,8,Fup listening to music. I've played
OL,9,Fmusic since I was maybe five, and to
OL,10,Fhave that as a part of my life is
OL,11,Freally special."
OL,13,FShe even took a keyboard to the Euros
OL,14,Fin Switzerland, where she became a
OL,15,Fglobal star and won the young player
OL,16,Fof the tournament award.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,F"I think we had so much time after
OL,8,Ftraining sessions, so if I was bored,
OL,9,FI'd keep playing, and even when I
OL,10,Fdidn't have that much time, I'd still
OL,11,Fplay because it's right next to my bed.
OL,13,F"So it was nice to calm down, settle
OL,14,Fand play the piano and just relax a
OL,15,Fbit, especially going into difficult
OL,16,Fgames."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FA strong faith is also a comfort for
OL,8,Fher during testing times. "Even though
OL,9,Fit seems difficult right now, there is
OL,10,Flight at the end of the tunnel and
OL,11,Fthere is a greater plan."
OL,13,FAgyemang also feels part of a growing
OL,14,Fcommunity in football, players who
OL,15,Fspeak openly about their beliefs.
OL,26,@sD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,F"I've seen it, especially in the
OL,8,FPremier League. You have Arsenal,
OL,9,FPalace, a lot of boys and even girls
OL,10,Fas well across the game that are
OL,11,Fexpressing their faith. And it's
OL,12,Freally refreshing to see that."
OL,14,FHer international breakout moment came
OL,15,Fseconds into her first England cap
OL,16,Fagainst Belgium in the spring last
OL,17,Fyear. Less than a minute after coming
OL,18,Fon as a substitute she scored a
OL,19,Fstunning goal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FShe tells me it's something she re-
OL,8,Flives on a regular basis.
OL,10,F"I think about it a lot. It's
OL,11,Funconventional, I think, to get called
OL,12,Fup at the last minute and then come
OL,13,Fon. I didn't expect to score in that
OL,14,Fmanner, but it was very nice to get
OL,15,Fthe opportunity and I'm always
OL,16,Fgrateful to Sarina for that.
OL,18,F"I just watch it sometimes on my phone
OL,19,Fwhen I'm bored. So it's nice to watch
OL,20,Fthat back and see that I was actually
OL,21,Fthere, and did that."
OL,26,@rD@AOUzD@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FWhat Agyemang achieved at the Euros
OL,8,Fmore than matched that early promise.
OL,9,FIn coming on as a substitute and
OL,10,Fscoring late goals, first against
OL,11,FSweden and then Italy, it's no
OL,12,Fexaggeration to say Agyemang saved
OL,13,FEngland's tournament.
OL,15,FWithout her the Lionesses would not
OL,16,Fhave retained their European title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FHer most memorable intervention came
OL,8,Fagainst Italy, deep into the stoppage
OL,9,Ftime. Her clinical finish forced the
OL,10,Fgame to extra time and halted an
OL,11,FEnglish exit.
OL,13,F"I think I celebrated a little bit. It
OL,14,Fwas nice to have the ball just fall at
OL,15,Fmy feet and I had quite a bit to do,
OL,16,Fbut I'm just happy that it went in the
OL,17,Fback of the net, and it was nice to
OL,18,Fsee the stadium absolutely buzzing and
OL,19,Fthe girls running across the pitch. I
OL,20,Fwas watching it back the other day and
OL,21,Fit's incredible."
OL,26,@uD@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIt tells you a lot about Agyemang's
OL,13,Fmodesty that celebrating a goal is
OL,14,Fsomething that doesn't come naturally
OL,15,Fto her.
OL,17,F"I've never really celebrated and when
OL,18,FI do, I don't like it, so I won't do
OL,19,Fit the next time. But yeah, we're
OL,20,Fworking on it. Maybe I'll think of
OL,21,Fsomething!"
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FShe'll need to if the early part of
OL,8,Fher career is anything to go by. Since
OL,9,Fthe Euros she's won award after award.
OL,10,FBut there's no danger that any of
OL,11,Fthose trinkets are going to her head.
OL,13,F"It's really nice to receive
OL,14,Frecognition, but I always say that
OL,15,Fwithout the team I can't achieve those
OL,16,Fawards. So, it's always nice to
OL,17,Fremember that I was part of a team
OL,18,Fwhich brought forth individual
OL,19,Fsuccess. And I guess my faith also
OL,20,Fkeeps me grounded in that aspect too."
OL,26,@uD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771887534
OL,3,C'We can win it': Agyemang on her ACL
OL,4,Crecovery, faith and 2027 World Cup
OL,5,Chopes
OL,7,FAnd that brings us to the World Cup
OL,8,Fnext year.
OL,10,F"I want to be there for that. There's
OL,11,Fone thing playing in the Euros, but
OL,12,Fthen going on the global scale,
OL,13,Fplaying in front of millions of fans
OL,14,Fin Brazil will be an incredible
OL,15,Fexperience."
OL,17,FAnd could the Lionesses lift that
OL,18,Ftrophy for the first time?
OL,19,F"Absolutely. We can win it, there's no
OL,20,Fdoubt about that."
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@LO]{D@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
